<br />
Which would be sort of defeatist.  The idea is to have the mob debuffed asap whilst not getting raped (assuming the mob doesn't rampage - in which case, why are you pulling anyway?! &lt;3 mem blur)  I almost always pull for any group I'm in, regardless of content.  Just tash, run back to group, and cast mem blur.  BUT in a situation where something is big and running too fast, etc, soothing words seems to do the trick.  The first level seems like more than enough to solve most aggro problems.  Anyone that needs a 10x insta-boggle probably deserves to die anyway /whistle.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
