                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This is my, "you break it, you tank it" AA.  It's quite nice at first level and instant recast allows you to run away from a mob that will possibly get you to low health aggro in one round if you stopped to boggle.  My only complaint is I can only do this every 36 min.
<br />

<br />
For dueling, this can be great I imagine.  Bring nasty hasted pet to duel.  They dispel magic on it and you do the pretend running around from your pet (well actually you aren't pretending), perfectly lining evil mob on your dueling opponent, hit soothing words, mob back on opponent (who was probably laughing at you running in circles and chain nuking, rooting, or whatever).
