                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">After some moderate testing, I'm not really impressed with Soothing Words 1.  The aggro reduction just isn't big enough - most of the time I find when someone has aggro, they're ahead by more than soothing words 1 will help with - or they'll be losing aggro in a second anyway.
<br />

<br />
Also, be careful with using this in raids.  If you time it wrong, you can make it harder for the tank that is struggling for aggro rather than easier.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
